Soft Skills\" con nuestro Simulador de Realidad Virtual! Ideal para profesionales que buscan mejorar sus habilidades interpersonales de forma inmersiva, interactiva y efectiva."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Softskills_Cover-Landscape-Padding.png", "id": "3682144288704654", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57570314_3682144292037987_5131369632409068623_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LZir9QxzIF0Q7kNvgEb7nSP&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAzlfCgp1zvz8_CuhF6O0-8fAm_64QPz22ikSmroph-Dg&oe=66F536FA"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Logo_8100x1296px.png", "id": "1994020534333698", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974910_1994020537667031_8688105079957652849_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2D8dVlBB4-QQ7kNvgGivE_b&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB-An9hLDicW-rbxYAoNrnt4xvdoiuqdmUPkuKV5iDiJw&oe=66F556C3"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-square_1440x1440px.png", "id": "1247184912914732", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035311_1247184916248065_2567077078745571082_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=dXlUaHyhkMEQ7kNvgFtz-Ap&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCW1Vgnpi2bJQjFyP5ncvGRABxWX5azbV6GZkqGENL7ag&oe=66F564F3"}, {"file_name": "INVELON_Icon-512x512px.png", "id": "1187254515612530", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974888_1187254518945863_7395065576696775988_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=rsS_K_PMUL8Q7kNvgGI27JV&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCiyKdoC1dNVolmHRy0beMJL8iAbf8rjEffCujxcq480g&oe=66F55540"}, {"file_name": "SoftSkills_Cover-portrait_1008x1440px.png", "id": "1151595012723300", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982662_1151595016056633_8079137566055371486_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid